{"title":"公社春景","authors":["张诚"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社春景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风已尽春来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社春景巧难描，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁牛高歌红旗舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山遍野泛春潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷一声天地动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花木发芽百草生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风抖开大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌水笑人欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管金鸡叫不叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾起铁牛下地了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出耕完千亩田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新土望着太阳笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春播"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗漫卷舞春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种机器响??，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进种子撒下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头笑看满田青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春晓田野雾蒙蒙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦苗尖上挂珠灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声起处银锄落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人面胜似桃花红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹得春雨下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨轻轻拍窗花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员屋内拣棉籽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔窗望雨笑哈哈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春灌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头黄莺报春音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦浇稀又追肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝麦海滚银水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来日金山托白云。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}